{"tid":1698691,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"紅磡站會否係黨鐵、狗官的死穴？","createTime":"2019-11-07T16:16:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-07T16:48:05.000Z","uid":283558,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"29a144b77f425d8d6d0f9c04f73a76098fc435ee","tid":1698691,"uid":283558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T16:16:02.000Z","msg":"有人記得中科興業、潘焯鴻嗎？<br />\n<br />\n中科想公開真相，<br />\n<br />\n想追究犯錯犯法的官及港鐵職員（當中必定包含虛假文書），<br />\n<br />\n而家眼前都有一個獨立調查委員會，<br />\n<br />\n不過，<br />\n<br />\n當大家忽略佢嘅存在，<br />\n<br />\n政府或港鐵高層偷偷地、靜悄悄地扭曲了獨立調查委員會的責任，並企圖或以圖把偷工減料並不按原來設計的工程的工程美化成：不完美、可接受。<br />\n<br />\n絕對明白香港每一天太多悲傷、荒謬、不合理的事情發生。<br />\n<br />\n但我仍然覺得，大家需要用時間及精神，了解一下現在進行的獨立調查委員會及中科現在所面對的困難。<br />\n<br />\n錯過呢次機會放生黨鐵及狗官，十分可惜。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/56ZFFZm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F56ZFFZm.jpg&h=0ad0c457&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1876680702389850/posts/2708420212549224?d=n&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1876680702389850%2Fposts%2F2708420212549224%3Fd%3Dn%26sfns%3Dmo&d=Z9XWEpuBYzNDjlwSEAyqKxPX6nNrjY8iteK6A9FjwF0%3D&h=0e17b657\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1876680702389850/posts/2708420212549224?d=n&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%B2%99%E4%B8%AD%E7%B6%AB%E5%81%B7%E5%B7%A5%E6%B8%9B%E6%96%99%E9%86%9C%E8%81%9E#%E6%B6%89%E4%BA%8B%E5%96%AE%E4%BD%8D%E5%8F%8A%E4%BA%BA%E7%89%A9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E6%25B2%2599%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%25B6%25AB%25E5%2581%25B7%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E6%25B8%259B%25E6%2596%2599%25E9%2586%259C%25E8%2581%259E%23%25E6%25B6%2589%25E4%25BA%258B%25E5%2596%25AE%25E4%25BD%258D%25E5%258F%258A%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%2589%25A9&d=Z9XWEpuBYzNDjlwSEAyqKxPX6nNrjY8iteK6A9FjwF0%3D&h=f09c6c20\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%B